{"type":"message","id":"ec708918","parentId":"eedb2f65","timestamp":"2026-03-20T03:45:10.716Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_aqzq3ewpceax_1","toolName":"session_status","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a)\n🕒 Time: Friday, March 20th, 2026 — 11:45 (Asia/Shanghai)\n🧠 Model: minimax/MiniMax-M2.7 · 🔑 api-key (minimax:cn)\n🧮 Tokens: 574 in / 175 out · 💵 Cost: $0.0005\n🗄️ Cache: 99% hit · 74k cached, 102 new\n📚 Context: 41k/200k (21%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n📊 Usage: 5h 25% left ⏱3h 14m\n🧵 Session: agent:main:cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d • updated just now\n⚙️ Runtime: direct · Think: off · elevated\n🪢 Queue: collect (depth 0)"}],"details":{"ok":true,"sessionKey":"agent:main:cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d","changedModel":false,"statusText":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a)\n🕒 Time: Friday, March 20th, 2026 — 11:45 (Asia/Shanghai)\n🧠 Model: minimax/MiniMax-M2.7 · 🔑 api-key (minimax:cn)\n🧮 Tokens: 574 in / 175 out · 💵 Cost: $0.0005\n🗄️ Cache: 99% hit · 74k cached, 102 new\n📚 Context: 41k/200k (21%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n📊 Usage: 5h 25% left ⏱3h 14m\n🧵 Session: agent:main:cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d • updated just now\n⚙️ Runtime: direct · Think: off · elevated\n🪢 Queue: collect (depth 0)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773978310714}}
